Nazar ka teeka buri nazar se bachaye,
Fevicol Teeka ID apno se milaye!

At Kumbh Mela, where millions gather, thousands often lose their way in the crowd. To help reunite lost individuals with their loved ones, Fevicol introduced a unique solution: Fevicol Teeka ID. A small yet powerful symbol of connection, ensuring no bond is ever broken💙

#KumbhMela2025 #FevicolKaJod #MazbootJod

Fevicol just gave Marol Naka Metro Station a sticky new identity! 🚌✨ Renamed in honour of its founder, Shri Balvantray Kalyanji Parekh, on his 101st birth anniversary, the station now celebrates Fevicol’s legacy with its funniest and most iconic ads.

Seen it yet? Tell us your favourite Fevicol ad in the comments! ⬇️
